Rebuild Mite_limitReport.jrxml to the production "Отчет по значениям до
корректировки" view: centered bold title, form code + date/report-time in the
top-right header (above the column headers), compact thin/dashed table, and the
"Должность, ФИО, подпись" footer. The per-row "Время" column is dropped (the time
now lives in the header). Adds the new "Контроль" column (green ✓ / red ✗).

The date/time is rendered in the page header with delayed group evaluation so it
sits above the column headers (not pushed below them by a group header band).

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 <noreply@anthropic.com>
